  "bug_fix_note": "EXQ-328 bug 1: seeded z_goal from obs_body[11] (pre-step benefit_exposure EMA). At resource contact, EMA has not yet been updated (obs_body is from BEFORE env.step()). This gave benefit_raw~0, effective_benefit<threshold, so seeding rarely fired. Fix: use raw harm_signal from env.step() directly. EXQ-328 bug 2: with benefit_threshold=0.1 and resource_benefit=0.5, raw contact benefit (0.5) exceeds threshold even without drive amplification (drive_weight=0). DRIVE_ABLATED would also seed z_goal, making C3 unmeasurable. Fix: set benefit_threshold=0.6 for DRIVE_ABLATED, above resource_benefit (0.5) but below amplified effective_benefit with DRIVE_ACTIVE (~0.8+ at drive_level=0.3). Also added MIN_WINDOW_STEPS guard and increased DRY_RUN_STEPS to 120."
